{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0003", "text": "在世界 我最軟弱 所以要他相擁", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 4, 5, 4, 5, 2, 9, 5, 4, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zoi6", "sai3", "gaai3", "ngo5", "zeoi3", "jyun5", "joek6", "so2", "ji5", "jiu3", "taa1", "jung2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "世界", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "軟弱", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "所以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "相擁", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0004", "text": "就讓我那懶懶身軀 躲進臂彎之中", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 5, 5, 5, 5, 3, 3, 9, 4, 4, 3, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zau6", "joeng6", "ngo5", "naa5", "laan5", "laan5", "san1", "keoi1", "do2", "zeon3", "bei3", "waan1", "zi1", "zung1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "就讓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "懶懶", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "身軀", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "躲進", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "臂彎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "之中", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0005", "text": "無論現實或是造夢 都給他每秒操縱", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 3, 3, 3, 5, 5, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mou4", "leon6", "jin6", "sat6", "waak6", "si6", "zou6", "mung6", "dou1", "kap1", "taa1", "mui5", "miu5", "cou1", "zung3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "無論", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "現實", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "或是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "造夢", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "每秒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "操縱", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0006", "text": "從來沒發覺 他的呼吸催促我變得多蠢", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 4, 4, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 5, 4, 3, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cung4", "loi4", "mut6", "faat3", "gok3", "taa1", "dik1", "fu1", "kap1", "ceoi1", "cuk1", "ngo5", "bin3", "dak1", "do1", "ceon2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "從來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發覺", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "呼吸", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "催促", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "變得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多蠢", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0007", "text": "誤信了我 弱質纖纖 隨便也感動", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 5, 5, 2, 3, 3, 3, 0, 2, 5, 9, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ng6", "seon3", "liu5", "ngo5", "joek6", "zat1", "cim1", "cim1", "ceoi4", "bin6", "jaa5", "gam2", "dung6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誤信", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "弱質", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "纖纖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "隨便", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "感動", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
