{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0011", "text": "無非別離 總是別離", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 8}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 2, 0, 9, 2, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mou4", "fei1", "bit6", "lei4", "zung2", "si6", "bit6", "lei4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "無非", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別離", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "總是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別離", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0012", "text": "失去他先知 我也可不需要那臂彎不哭 也不生氣", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 20}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 4, 3, 3, 3, 5, 5, 9, 3, 3, 4, 5, 4, 3, 3, 3, 5, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["sat1", "heoi3", "taa1", "sin1", "zi1", "ngo5", "jaa5", "ho2", "bat1", "seoi1", "jiu3", "naa5", "bei3", "waan1", "bat1", "huk1", "jaa5", "bat1", "sang1", "hei3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "失去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "先知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "需要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "臂彎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不哭", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "生氣", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0013", "text": "我最初天天 只等他將體溫軀去我寒意", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 3, 3, 3, 9, 9, 3, 3, 9, 3, 3, 4, 5, 0, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "zeoi3", "co1", "tin1", "tin1", "zi2", "dang2", "taa1", "zoeng1", "tai2", "wan1", "keoi1", "heoi3", "ngo5", "hon4", "ji3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最初", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "等", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "體溫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "軀去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "寒意", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0014", "text": "還承認我太怕冷要靠愛侶輸出暖意", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 5, 4, 4, 5, 4, 4, 4, 5, 3, 3, 5, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["waan4", "sing4", "jing6", "ngo5", "taai3", "paa3", "laang5", "jiu3", "kaau3", "oi3", "leoi5", "syu1", "ceot1", "nyun5", "ji3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "承認", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怕冷", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "靠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛侶", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "輸出", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "暖意", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0015", "text": "誰料到今天只得一個 仍然可以生活", "structure": {"line_index": 15, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 4, 3, 3, 9, 3, 3, 4, 0, 0, 9, 5, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "liu6", "dou3", "gam1", "tin1", "zi2", "dak1", "jat1", "go3", "jing4", "jin4", "ho2", "ji5", "sang1", "wut6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "料到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "今天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍然", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "生活", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "多得他", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1116", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0014", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0016", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
